wouldn't want to go to school.

17:24.339 --> 17:26.025
That learning would be boring.

17:26.050 --> 17:27.230
But you make it fun.

17:28.230 --> 17:29.276
Well...

17:29.777 --> 17:31.856
she's my favorite student.

17:32.332 --> 17:33.476
Don't tell anyone.

