18:25.607 --> 18:27.026
Or if they can be trusted.

18:27.779 --> 18:28.936
If they get caught,

18:29.115 --> 18:30.186
will they talk?

18:30.211 --> 18:31.294
'Cause if that happens,

18:31.319 --> 18:32.832
your career will be over.

18:33.309 --> 18:34.736
You'll never be able to practice law.

18:34.737 --> 18:36.489
You might even face criminal charges.

18:36.514 --> 18:40.129
What's unethical is that I.A.
never made the investigation public

18:40.154 --> 18:42.615
and Wilson chose to keep
these files redacted.

18:42.640 --> 18:43.787
Why would he do that

18:43.812 --> 18:45.213
if he wasn't protecting the police?

18:45.490 --> 18:47.887
You don't know if he
made some deal to get

18:47.912 --> 18:49.281
his son's charges dropped.

18:49.647 --> 18:50.736
You could be wrong.

18:50.737 --> 18:53.059
And you'd be betraying
Wilson, your clerkship,

18:53.084 --> 18:55.208
