22:23.277 --> 22:25.423
Is it true Evan took
an interest in Amanda,

22:25.448 --> 22:26.783
and greenlit her app,

22:26.808 --> 22:28.897
and then all of a sudden, she was gone?

22:29.237 --> 22:31.054
