24:23.107 --> 24:25.991
How did you get all
the men's salaries info?

24:26.016 --> 24:27.316
I can't reveal my source.

24:27.317 --> 24:28.875
No question, we put it all out there.

24:28.900 --> 24:30.526
- Internally.
- No, online.

24:30.527 --> 24:32.066
Expose the whole tech community.

24:32.067 --> 24:33.896
- Totally, yes.
- Wait, hold on.

24:33.897 --> 24:36.599
if we publicly shame Speckulate,

24:36.624 --> 24:38.106
the company's revenues could suffer

24:38.107 --> 24:39.937
and then we could all be out of a job.

24:40.897 --> 24:42.026
I'm willing to risk it.

24:42.467 --> 24:43.646
