25:08.240 --> 25:09.336
I just can't do it.

25:16.687 --> 25:18.176
Mariana, you have a lot to lose, too.

25:18.977 --> 25:22.107
- You just got your app idea greenlit.
- Yeah, but...

25:23.147 --> 25:25.186
But this is bigger than my career.

25:25.187 --> 25:27.237
This is about doing what's right.

25:28.527 --> 25:29.976
Let's put the list out there.

25:29.977 --> 25:32.356
- Yeah.
- All right.

26:01.437 --> 26:03.736
I understand that Mom was overwhelmed

26:05.056 --> 26:07.356
with two kids, as a single parent,

26:07.357 --> 26:09.397
workin' two jobs, 16 hours a day.

26:14.574 --> 26:16.186
I remember the good times

26:16.949 --> 26:18.637
before the drugs and the alcohol.

26:24.027 --> 26:25.746
I understand...

26:26.561 --> 26:29.040
why she went to them for relief.

26:30.855 --> 26:32.019
Life is hard...

26:33.776 --> 26:34.878
especially...

26:36.003 --> 26:37.816
for people like us who

26:38.582 --> 26:40.692
are living in a world
of white supremacy,

26:42.083 --> 26:45.336
in a world that can treat us
like we're less than human.

26:46.309 --> 26:48.258
I understand.

26:51.857 --> 26:53.737
You and Mom were at peace.

26:55.546 --> 26:56.742
