28:14.410 --> 28:15.830
I'll always be your best friend.

28:17.856 --> 28:20.330
And you know, it took a lot of
guts to call off the wedding.

28:21.635 --> 28:24.236
Even though someone spent hours

28:24.237 --> 28:26.337
painstakingly planning the whole thing.

28:27.900 --> 28:29.040
I'm sorry.

28:29.357 --> 28:33.888
But you should marry anyone that
you're not 100% sure is "the one."

28:39.937 --> 28:41.093
I know...

28:43.414 --> 28:44.606
It's all here.

28:44.607 --> 28:47.236
You can't leak those files
