31:14.080 --> 31:16.643
in a disgraceful breach of privacy,

31:16.668 --> 31:19.518
posted a list of Speckulate
employee salaries online.

31:19.799 --> 31:20.976
Now, we called this meeting

31:21.375 --> 31:24.360
to demand that if anybody knows
who perpetrated this...

31:24.805 --> 31:25.896
theft...

31:25.897 --> 31:27.180
of company data,

31:27.205 --> 31:28.405
we want to hear from them now.

31:31.438 --> 31:32.816
Let me put this another way.

31:32.817 --> 31:34.048
All right?

31:34.073 --> 31:35.522
This is a...

31:36.633 --> 31:39.122
huge PR problem

31:39.420 --> 31:40.466
for this company.

31:40.491 --> 31:41.927
