32:10.112 --> 32:12.186
a long time ago, and, uh,

32:12.187 --> 32:14.861
I think what we should do,

32:15.165 --> 32:16.290
is to...

32:16.673 --> 32:17.792
hold her accountable.

32:18.431 --> 32:19.476
So...

32:19.477 --> 32:20.626
Angela...

32:21.175 --> 32:22.624
I'm sorry to do this publically

32:22.649 --> 32:23.887
- but you are...
