33:23.334 --> 33:24.446
is what this is.

33:25.031 --> 33:26.336
I am the victim!

33:27.669 --> 33:28.858
Morning.

33:29.514 --> 33:31.877
Are the plaintiffs ready
to call their next witness?

33:32.796 --> 33:33.965
Yes, your Honor.

33:34.486 --> 33:35.846
The plaintiffs would like to call

33:35.871 --> 33:37.660
Officer Griffin to the
stand at this time.

33:52.282 --> 33:53.306
