Griffin is not in evidence.

34:13.364 --> 34:14.905
You ruled to keep it under seal.

34:14.929 --> 34:16.496
What are you up to, Ms. Walker?

34:16.697 --> 34:19.512
- New evidence has come to light.
- We'd like to request a recess

34:19.536 --> 34:22.172
until tomorrow to, uh,
evaluate this evidence.

34:29.991 --> 34:32.371
Hey, it's Sandra, can I come in?

34:47.603 --> 34:49.043
I'm sorry I didn't make it to court.

35:02.372 --> 35:03.852
