- I'm sorry.

35:24.892 --> 35:26.061
You know, I, um...

35:27.312 --> 35:30.424
I gave you the wrong advice when I
said we couldn't have our moments.

35:31.573 --> 35:32.846
That we had to be strong.

35:33.698 --> 35:36.377
That... that black superwoman complex.

35:40.061 --> 35:41.275
We don't have to be that.

35:42.928 --> 35:44.208
We can just be real.

35:46.556 --> 35:47.735
We can break down.

35:48.726 --> 35:51.896
We can... We can ask for help.

35:54.531 --> 35:57.867
We can be there for our
sisters, and brothers.

35:59.307 --> 36:00.566
The way you were there for me.

36:08.623 --> 36:09.880
Hey, so,

36:10.437 --> 36:11.740
I want to be honest with you.

36:12.890 --> 36:15.970
