administrative side of things,

36:43.505 --> 36:44.836
so I had no idea that

36:45.374 --> 36:47.452
women weren't getting
paid the same as men.

36:47.477 --> 36:51.023
But I plan to correct
that, and get rid of Josh.

36:53.788 --> 36:54.908
Please don't leave.

36:57.805 --> 36:58.891
Thank you, but...

37:00.357 --> 37:01.625
I think I have to.

37:04.632 --> 37:07.030
You know maybe I'll develop
my app on my own.

37:08.475 --> 37:09.644
On your own?

37:09.669 --> 37:13.403
Well, yeah, maybe I'll set up
a GoFundMe page or something.

37:15.560 --> 37:16.731
M-Mariana...

37:18.647 --> 37:21.050
if you choose to
leave, I can't stop you.

37:21.597 --> 37:23.402
But you can't take your app with you.

37:24.995 --> 37:27.573
Every idea you had under
contract here belongs to me.

37:36.532 --> 37:38.704
- Hello?
- Hi.

37:39.111 --> 37:41.361
- It's me.
- Where the hell are you?

37:45.924 --> 37:48.332
I drove out to this cliff, by the beach.

37:51.721 --> 37:53.006
I was gonna drive off.

37:53.706 --> 37:55.356
One of the voices that I...

37:56.027 --> 37:58.166
kept hearing in my head was yours.

37:59.277 --> 38:00.406
Really?

38:01.837 --> 38:02.996
What was I saying?

38:03.021 --> 38:05.165
- "Do it."
- Shut up.

38:09.399 --> 38:10.879
